# Documentation Reconciliation Plan

## Current State (Reality Check)

### What Actually Exists
1. **Core Systems (Gates 1-5)** ✅
   - PyQt6/Pygame integration with stable 62 FPS
   - Full preference system (Cobb-Douglas, Linear, Leontief)
   - Grid with deterministic resource management
   - Decision mode with tie-breaking and epsilon bootstrap
